## How to Run Locally

### Prerequisites
- Node.js (v14+ recommended)   
- Polkadot.js extension  
- KILT Protocol SDK  

### Steps
```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/<your-repo>.git
cd <your-project-folder>

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start the backend
npm run backend

# Start the frontend
npm start
```
